<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="leisure-n">leisure <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'leʒə(r)/    美 /'liːʒər/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>闲暇；业余时间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>leisure time / activities</strong>
闲暇时间/活动</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the leisure industry</strong>
休闲娱乐行业</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-ones-leisure">at one's leisure</h3>
<p>1.<strong>有空时；空闲时：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tibetan antelopes are moving under the bridge, with some stopping to eat grass at their leisure.
藏羚羊在桥下活动，有的停下来悠闲地吃草。</p><footer>外研新选必① – 6</footer></div></div>